# â­ diff-risk-dashboard â€” APV â†’ Risk Summary (Python CLI)

A lean, production-grade **Python CLI** that ingests **ai-patch-verifier (APV)** JSON and outputs a clear **risk summary** in **JSON** or **Markdown**.

